id="post-2324" class="post-2324 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-direct-action category-environment tag-collaboration tag-environment tag-estonia tag-garbage"><h2 class="entry-title"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/2010/02/12/estonia-cleans-up/" title="Permalink to Estonia Cleans Up!" rel="bookmark">Estonia Cleans Up!</a></h2><div
class="entry-meta"> <span
class="entry-date" title="2010/02/12 3:05 pm"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/2010/02/12/estonia-cleans-up/" title="Estonia Cleans Up!" rel="bookmark">2010/02/12 3:05 pm</a></span><span
class="entry-meta-sep"> / </span><span
class="entry-author author vcard"><a
href="http://www.thingsaregood.com/author/fono/" title="by Fono" rel="author">Fono</a></span></div><div
class="entry-content clearfix"><p>You probably didn&#8217;t hear about it, but in 2008 Estonia cleaned up <strong>10,000 tons of trash</strong> in their forests by recruiting <strong>50,000 people</strong>. How? Through an extensive media campaign and a good dose of networked collaboration.</p><p>The &#8220;Let&#8217;s Do It!&#8221; website is <a
href="http://www.teeme2008.ee/">here</a>, but in Estonian. So here&#8217;s a video in English!</p><p><object
width="425" height="344"><param
name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/A5GryIDl0qY&#038;hl=en_US&#038;fs=1&#038;"></param><param
name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><param
name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"></param><embed
src="http://www.youtube.com/v/A5GryIDl0qY&#038;hl=en_US&#038;fs=1&#038;" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true" width="425" height="344"></embed></object></p><p>Based on the success in Estonia, the campaign has gone <a
href='http://www.letsdoitworld.org/en'>worldwide</a>!</p><div
class='sharedaddy sd-block sd-like jetpack-likes-widget-wrapper jetpack-likes-widget-unloaded' id='like-post-wrapper-1111807-2324-5384d3b3d5dbb' data-src='//widgets.wp.com/likes/#blog_id=1111807&amp;post_id=2324&amp;origin=www.thingsaregood.com&amp;obj_id=1111807-2324-5384d3b3d5dbb' data-name='like-post-frame-1111807-2324-5384d3b3d5dbb'><h3 class='sd-title'>Like this:</h3><div
